column5: I went to see Larry the Cable Guy tonight. Man, that is one funny dude. I'm a big fan and almost drove to Minneapolis to see him last year. I was surprised that he did a show here in Thunder Bay. He sold out two shows in the first day. If you ever get the chance, and like to laugh, go see this guy.
was this televised? and ya, he's a super funny guy! i wouldnt mind goin to see him some day!
I hear him all the time on xm.There is much more to him than Git er done.He is a pretty fart smeller.
